TWA
EMPLOYEES' TIMETABLE
INTERNATIONAL SCHEDULES
ISSUE DATE JANUARY 31, 1975
Transmittal 3-75
EFFECTIVE FEBRUARY 23, 1975
(Except as Noted)
TRANS WORLD
Holidays 75
TWA's Exclusive Holidays '75 Program is designed for independent leisure
travellers -- and is fully commissionable at 10% to travel agents.
Remind
your agents of this valuable program and its commissions.
Holidays USA (10% Commissionable to Agents)
This new tour book offers exciting ways to see the U.S.A. Freestyle Tours
in 10 great cities. Freewheeler West and East.
Motorcoach Tours.
Canyonlands.
TrekAmerica Tours. Dude Ranch Holidays. All backed
by TWA's Tour Warranty.
Hotelpass USA/Canada (10% Commissionable to Agents)
Guaranteed accommodations without reservations in 30 cities.
Room rates
start at a low U.S. $8.75 per person. Choice of three hotel categories.
Little Black Book
A TWA extra for 17 worldwide cities.
It's packed with coupons good for
discounts and savings on meals, beverages, admissions, and merchandise.
Getaway Guides
Authoritative and lively, they give valuable information on the sights to see,
places to go, and off beat attractions only a local resident would know.
There are 15 Guides available, at U.S. $1.50 each.
